com.arjuna.mw.wsas.status
Interface Status

All Known Implementing Classes:
Completed, Completing, NoActivity, Active, Created, Unknown, XAStatus, Confirming, Cancelled, CancelOnly, Cancelling, Confirmed, HeuristicHazard, HeuristicMixed, Prepared, HeuristicConfirm, HeuristicCancel, Preparing, XAStatus, Coordinating, RollingBack, RollbackOnly, NoTransaction, Committed, RolledBack, Committing
public interface Status

This interface is the basis for all statuses that the activity can go through. Services are expected to extend this in specific ways. Uniqueness is guaranteed by the package scope of the final implementation.
